{"tid":108571,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"女學神撞石壆四輪朝天","createTime":"2017-02-05T11:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T11:52:36.000Z","uid":14197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da26c70c73d8654cae460feb02efb49980514ea5","tid":108571,"uid":14197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KT1r0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KT1r0L.jpg&h=28c822a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，一名24歲女學神沿荃灣青山公路進行駕駛練習，駛至大窩口支路時，懷疑猶豫不決，失控撞向路中石壆後向右翻側，教車師傅與女學神一度被困，其後自行爬出車廂。女學神手腳受傷需要送院治理，姓馬的教車師傅表示由於事出突然，坦言「一秒鐘嘅時間真係反應唔到」，所以來不及煞車而釀成意外。<br />\n<br />\n香港汽車工業學會會長李耀培稱學神並未學滿師，所以因不小心引起意外警方也較少會作檢控，反而教車師傅要負責的機會較大，因師傅有經驗兼有專用腳掣可煞停學神的車。《蘋果》翻查資料，2013年曾有男途人被學神駕車撞斃，結果學神與七旬教車師傅同樣不小心駕駛罪成，兩師徒同被判150小時會服務令及停牌半年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170204/56261635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170204%2F56261635&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP93Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7647d223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170204%2F56261635&h=bc98dffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170204/56261635</a>"},{"pid":"79688f7f1fbf3470ebd67c7c8c194c45fee45412","tid":108571,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"連登啲死毒撚咪又係淨係識屌女人揸車 或者 留意張相啲腳指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486682961d7f00d26ced64132769cf3c35da5ccd","tid":108571,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登啲死毒撚咪又係淨係識屌女人揸車 或者 留意張相啲腳指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救護員既屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278eaf7aa3c9732c51173df22492932099425a20","tid":108571,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"釘9個師傅牌啦"},{"pid":"193f743759cfac64a0e87e1c5b232fd6e26155c7","tid":108571,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，一名唔知自己做乜鳩的女學神沿荃灣青山公路進行駕駛練習，駛至大窩口支路時，懷疑因為自己痴撚左線係到諗轉唔轉線，搞到部車撞向路中石壆後向右翻側"},{"pid":"b1af507aa8a58015040db1517b4a8761a3468ef6","tid":108571,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下午4時許，一名唔知自己做乜鳩的女學神沿荃灣青山公路進行駕駛練習，駛至大窩口支路時，懷疑因為自己痴撚左線係到諗轉唔轉線，搞到部車撞向路中石壆後向右翻側</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0c03c41be40b832dfddd2b759eb98cade7f354","tid":108571,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"女人唔好揸車啦"},{"pid":"d85a1b97a2a35f95392f8b4ed48d53af0961062b","tid":108571,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}